    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and cut your <strong>red onion[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half</p><p>Chop <strong>half</strong> your <strong>onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Dice the <strong>remaining onion</strong> finely</p>",
